    "To address this objective, an ADMF method is introduced.",
    "The overarching architecture depicted in Fig. 5 encompasses the construction of three unrelated 3S channels: sequential, syntactic, and semantic, aimed at encapsulating distinct text properties.",
    "Subsequently, enhancement algorithms within each channel were proposed to facilitate the amalgamation of information across various graphs.",
    "For instance, the unrelated sequence graph UG seq enhanced multichannel entails three primary layers:",
    "Layer 1: Initial assignment of different weights based on the significance of syntactic and semantic channel representations within the sequence."
